attributes.title: Terms and Conditions
attributes.review: Doesn’t take responsibility for third parties but entire app is saturated with “third parties”. How are we supposed to be sure about the validity of the information or the security of our information. If everything is going to a third party but they don’t take responsibility for third party information then they basically disown responsibility for the entire app. I’m disappointed that Apple allows loopholes like this and doesn’t make app creators responsible for non-open source software. Especially software that’s responsible for providing political information for POTUS. The TLDR of the T&C is that the app doesn’t take responsibility for anything. The app reserves the right to edit your posted content. If you post something they reserve the right to change your words rather then just delete your post. This whole situation is f***ed up in my opinion.
